nodes.text: Younglings is a short comic story published in Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.25, and later in Star Wars: The Clone Wars Magazine 8.

Even in the middle of war, the training of the next generation of Jedi can't be overlooked… When a nocturnal expedition takes an unexpected turn in the latest issue's brand new comic strip, Anakin needs the help of some 'Younglings'!
